            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Ratcliff Highway. On the 9th and 15th of May, a coat and a pair of trowsers were pawned in the name of Johnson.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I agreed to take his bag to the vessel for him.</p>
